Welcome to the MapHub Portal project (suggestions for better names welcome!)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

BASICS
------
This is a Grails project (http://grails.org/)


FIRST STEPS
-----------
1. Clone the repository
2. In the "grails-app/conf" folder, locate the file "DataSource.groovy.template". 
   Create a copy of this file named "DataSource.groovy" and edit the contents to
   match your local database settings.